data.description: Best of both worlds! This beautiful 2 bedroom, 1 baths condo with hardwood flooring throughout and deeded one-car attached garage sits on a quiet residential street with views to the tree-filled courtyard. Yet it's across the street from a new, high end grocery store, and just half a block from the dining and shopping on North Avenue. Enjoy urban convenience, suburban peace and quiet, and River Forest Schools, all at an unbeatable price. FHA Approved!
